f=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das <strong>HTML <code>&lt;dl&gt;</code> Element</strong> (oder <em>HTML</em> <em>Description List Element</em>) umfasst eine Liste von Begriffspaaren und Beschreibungen. Üblicherweise wird das Element zur Implementierung eines Glossars oder zur Anzeige von Metadaten (eine Liste von Schlüsselwertpaaren) genutzt.</p>\n\n<p>Vor HTML5, war &lt;dl&gt; bekannt als Definition List.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Inhaltskategorien</a></th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">Fließender Inhalt</a>, wenn das <code>&lt;dl&gt;</code> Elementkind nur ein Wertepaar beinhaltet, dann greifbarer Inhalt.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubter Inhalt</th>\n   <td>Null oder mehr <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dt\"><code>&lt;dt&gt;</code></a> Elemente, jedes gefolgt von einem oder mehreren <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dd\"><code>&lt;dd&gt;</code></a> Elementen.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Tag Auslassung</th>\n   <td>Keine, sowohl das Anfangs- als auch das End-Tag sind erforderlich.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubte Elternelemente</th>\n   <td>Jedes Element, das <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">fließenden Inhalt</a> erlaubt.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM Schnittstelle</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLDListElement\"><code>HTMLDListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">Dieses Element schließt </span><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">globale Attribute</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\"> ein.</span></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"compact\"><a id=\"attr-compact\" href=\"#attr-compact\"><b><code>compact</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Zwingt die Beschreibung dazu, in derselben Linie zu erscheinen wie der Begriff. Dieses Attribut wird aktuell nicht unterstützt.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"einzelbegriff_und_beschreibung","title":"Einzelbegriff und Beschreibung","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Firefox<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>A free, open source, cross-platform, graphical web browser\n      developed by the Mozilla Corporation and hundreds of volunteers.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- other terms and definitions --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Ausgabe:</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"Image:HTML-dl1.png\" src=\"/@api/deki/files/241/=HTML-dl1.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"multiple_begriffe_einzelne_beschreibung","title":"Multiple Begriffe, einzelne Beschreibung","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Firefox<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Mozilla Firefox<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Fx<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>A free, open source, cross-platform, graphical web browser\n      developed by the Mozilla Corporation and hundreds of volunteers.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- other terms and definitions --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Ausgabe:</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"Image:HTML-dl2.png\" src=\"/@api/deki/files/242/=HTML-dl2.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"einzelbegriff_multiple_beschreibungen","title":"Einzelbegriff, multiple Beschreibungen","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Firefox<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>A free, open source, cross-platform, graphical web browser\n      developed by the Mozilla Corporation and hundreds of volunteers.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>The Red Panda also known as the Lesser Panda, Wah, Bear Cat or Firefox,\n      is a mostly herbivorous mammal, slightly larger than a domestic cat\n      (60 cm long).<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- other terms and definitions --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Ausgabe:</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"Image:HTML-dl3.png\" src=\"/@api/deki/files/243/=HTML-dl3.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"multiple_begriffe_und_beschreibungen","title":"Multiple Begriffe und Beschreibungen","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Es ist ebenfalls möglich, multiple Begriffe und Beschreibungen zu definieren, wenn man die oberen Beispiele kombiniert.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"metadata","title":"Metadata","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Description Lists sind nützlich um Metadaten als Wertepaar-Listen anzuzeigen.</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;dl&gt;\n    &lt;dt&gt;Name&lt;/dt&gt;\n    &lt;dd&gt;Godzilla&lt;/dd&gt;\n    &lt;dt&gt;Born&lt;/dt&gt;\n    &lt;dd&gt;1952&lt;/dd&gt;\n    &lt;dt&gt;Birthplace&lt;/dt&gt;\n    &lt;dd&gt;Japan&lt;/dd&gt;\n    &lt;dt&gt;Color&lt;/dt&gt;\n    &lt;dd&gt;Green&lt;/dd&gt;\n&lt;/dl&gt;\n</pre>\n\n<p>Tipp: Es kann hilfreich sein, Separatoren für Schlüsselwerte in CSS3 zu definieren, wie zum Beispiel:</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">dt:after</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\": \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"anmerkungen","title":"Anmerkungen","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Weder dieses Element, noch das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a> Element, sollten genutzt werden, um bloß eine Einrückung vorzunehmen. Es funktioniert zwar, wird in der Praxis jedoch nicht angewendet und verfehlt die Definition einer Description List.</p>\n\n<p>Um die Einrückung eines Begriffs zu ändern, sollte die <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS\" title=\"CSS\">CSS</a> <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/margin\"><code>margin</code></a> Eigenschaft genutzt werden.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/grouping-content.html#the-dl-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;dl&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/grouping-content.html#the-dl-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;dl&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/struct/lists.html#h-10.3\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;dl&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Ursprüngliche Definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Browser Kompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Merkmal</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Grundlegende Unterstützung</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Merkmal</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Grundlegende Unterstützung</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dt\"><code>&lt;dt&gt;</code></a> Element</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dd\"><code>&lt;dd&gt;</code></a> Element</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect5\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Attribute","id":"attribute"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Anmerkungen","id":"anmerkungen"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das HTML <dl> Element (oder HTML Description List Element) umfasst eine Liste von Begriffspaaren und Beschreibungen. Üblicherweise wird das Element zur Implementierung eines Glossars oder zur Anzeige von Metadaten (eine Liste von Schlüsselwertpaaren) genutzt.","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<dl>: The Description List element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"dl","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<dl> : l'élément de liste de descriptions","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<dl>: 説明リスト要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<dl>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"dl","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"dl","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<dl>: Элемент списка описаний","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<dl>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/html/element/dl","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/html/element/dl/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dl","title":"<dl>"}],"pageTitle":"<dl> - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}